a Tag with sharks.\n\nThe VR controls are super responsive (it feels like a human-shark mind meld): simply look where you want the shark to swim. Pull the trigger to move forward, press the grip button to chomp/eat things.", "short_description": "Eat your friends in 'SHARKS' a cross-platform (PC and VR) multiplayer hunting game. Hunt with groups of up to 10 people online. Eat whatever you can to survive and avoid the zombie sharks: last player standing wins. It's like Gorilla Tag with sharks."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://ezone.com/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Ezone PTY LTD", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://ezone.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "MULTI_USER", "CO_OP"], "id": "219944073774624"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 2, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "245104471462418"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1006562187377203"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "245104471462418"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1720481722, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "245104471462418"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "28531348619785530", "version": "0.1"}, "id": "601272338109301", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "9571468216200189", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "28531348619785530"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "601272338109301"}]}, "change_log": "Release Notes - v0.1.12 - \"EXPLOSIONS AND ELF HATS\"\n\nWe've reworked the physics so now you can have even more fun with cannonballs and exploding air tanks. Create traps and set off chain reactions to slowdown other sharks. And while you're exploding other sharks get into the holiday spirit with a free gift from us - a special limited edition Elf Hat!\n\nNew:\n- Free Elf Hat (for a limited time!)\n- Scuba tank now a biteable and throwable bomb\n- Explosions cause chain reactions\n- Moveable items react to explosions\n- More diver Dad jokes\n- Above ocean elements (see if you can access them!)\n\nFixes:\n- Damage caused by explosions proportional to distance\n- Skins purchased outside the game are auto-activated \n- Players outside the map fix\n- Tweaked goldfish rewards\n- Multiplayer updated (so make sure you're friends update too so you can play on the same servers)\n\nIf you love playing SHARKS then get the GOLD Founders Skin to show your support. All proceeds from skins go right back into the game: new game modes, customizable items, maps, interactable creatures and objects and multiplayer servers.\n\nThanks so much for playing and please tell your friends: word of mouth is the best way to get more players in the game!\n\nIf you have any feedback or comments, please come chat in the Discord (https://ezone.com/discord). Cheers!\n\n- Simon and Jamie", "created_date": 1732697605, "id": "28531348619785530", "version": "0.1", "version_code": 12, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "9571468216200189", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "28531348619785530"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "601272338109301"}]}, "change_log": "Release Notes - v0.1l - \"FOUNDERS SKIN\"\n\nIn this release we've added an exclusive limited edition FOUNDERS SKIN for the Meta Quest that turns your shark into a solid gold shiny beast.\n\nIf you love playing SHARKS then get this skin to show your support. All proceeds go right back into the game: new game modes, customizable items, maps, interactable creatures and objects and multiplayer servers.\n\nNew:\n- Gold Founders Skin for Meta Quest\n- Win reward: goldfish spawned near leaderboard - the more you win, the more you get!\n- Stats: kills, bites, wins, eaten objects + more\n- Online leaderboards and achievements\n- Updated menus\n- Improved unlocked chest graphics\n\nFixes:\n- Multiplayer: game round start bug fix\n- Rocket powerup more responsive\n- More accurate online player count\n- Improved fade-in-out between scenes\n- Increased health from eating some fish", "created_date": 1732179687, "id": "28470653645855028", "version": "0.1", "version_code": 11, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "9571468216200189", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "28531348619785530"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "601272338109301"}]}, "change_log": "Release Notes - v0.1k - \"HEALTH UI\"\n\nIn this release we've added onscreen health UI so you can see how much damage you are causing and how much health you receive for food.\n\n- Health UI\n- HUD always active\n\nFixes:\n- Removed HUD toggle from settings\n\nAs we get further along we'll be looking for more feedback regarding gameplay, etc, but for now we just want to make sure everyone can get started and that the multiplayer is solid. If you have any feedback or comments, please direct them to the Discord. Cheers!\n\n- Simon and Jamie", "created_date": 1717484016, "id": "26440873605499719", "version": "0.1", "version_code": 10, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "9571468216200189", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "28531348619785530"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "601272338109301"}]}, "change_log": "Release Notes - v0.1j - \"HOT FIX\"\n\nFixes:\n- drop bitten object if another shark takes it\n- option to invert y-axis in settings\n- menu tweaks", "created_date": 1709015848, "id": "25657108930542861", "version": "0.1", "version_code": 9, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "9571468216200189", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "28531348619785530"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "601272338109301"}]}, "change_log": "Release Notes - v0.1i - \"BITE CLUB\"\n\nIn this release we've added the ability to bite and grab objects so you can move them around the environment. See if you can find the biteable diver (complete with sharkproof wetsuit)!\n\n- Bite objects and drag them around (hold the bite button)\n- The heavier the object you are biting/carrying the slower you go\n- Throw bitten objects (flick your head and release the bite button)\n- Cannonballs explode when they hit something\n- Explosions impact nearby sharks\n- Treasure Chests: complete quests to unlock rewards\n- Unlock more items:  1:10 chance for 'Rare', 1:50 for 'Epic', 1:100 for 'Legendary'\n\nFixes:\n- Changed food outline color to green\n- Hazard outline color to red\n- Hazards disabled for longer after you hit them\n\nComing Soon:\n\n- More powerups: invincibility, friggin inlaserbility!\n- More items and skins\n- More game maps and modes\n\nAs we get further along we'll be looking for more feedback regarding gameplay, etc, but for now we just want to make sure everyone can get started and that the multiplayer is solid. If you have any feedback or comments, please direct them to the Discord. Cheers!\n\n- Simon and Jamie", "created_date": 1708912663, "id": "25647459008174520", "version": "0.1", "version_code": 8, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}]}}, "viewer": {"user": null}}}